title: Coronavirus deaths top 5,000 in US as more states issue stay-at-home orders
description: Grim news of coronavirus infections and fatalities continued in the U.S. on Wednesday, with the number of confirmed cases rising above 200,000 and the number of deaths surpassing 5,000.
